description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Sussex Partnership NHS Foundation Trust CAMHS / LACHMS&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Child and Adolescent Psychotherapist or Systemic Psychotherapist&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt; Band 7, 22.5 hours per week &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A new opportunity has arisen to appoint either a part-time Child and Adolescent Psychotherapist or Systemic Psychotherapist to our Looked After Children’s CAMHS Team. The successful applicant will work across our multi-disciplinary team providing CAMH services to looked after children in partnership with our Local Authority. These services have the remit of improving placement stability and relationships between children, young people, and their carers. The team has already established creative working relationships across health and social care.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The team is part of East Sussex Children and Young People mental health services. Clinical supervision and support will be provided from a senior practitioner of their discipline as well as supervision in place for the team and the opportunity to meet regularly with their own therapeutic modality across the county. There is access to career development and training.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post will be based in East Sussex CAMHS bases alongside Local Authority LAC and Fostering bases. The remit for the successful candidate will be to focus directly on clinical work with looked after children, their carers, and the networks supporting them. There will be scope for brief and intensive interventions, specialist assessments and consultations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post would suit a confident and experienced ACP registered Child and Adolescent Psychotherapist or Systemic Psychotherapist with generic and/or specialist CAMHS experience who is capable of autonomous team working, adapting their specialist skills as required.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name Linda Winchester&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job titleChild and Adolescent Psychotherapist and Clinical Lead for LAC&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address Linda.Winchester@sussexpartnership.nhs.uk&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number 07738 758400&lt;/p&gt;
